{"tid":1010524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"網民熱話：惡男企門口阻客 髮型師勸讓不成掀罵戰","createTime":"2019-02-06T05:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T06:02:50.000Z","uid":56881,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f3940242c8db74b51c66a2897d5a97d72fc5c61c","tid":1010524,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T05:02:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E6%83%A1%E7%94%B7%E4%BC%81%E9%96%80%E5%8F%A3%E9%98%BB%E5%AE%A2-%E9%AB%AE%E5%9E%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%8B%B8%E8%AE%93%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E6%8E%80%E7%BD%B5%E6%88%B0-104906536.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E6%2583%25A1%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25BC%2581%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%258F%25A3%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25AE%25A2-%25E9%25AB%25AE%25E5%259E%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%258B%25B8%25E8%25AE%2593%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%258E%2580%25E7%25BD%25B5%25E6%2588%25B0-104906536.html&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=d4a1f5cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E6%83%A1%E7%94%B7%E4%BC%81%E9%96%80%E5%8F%A3%E9%98%BB%E5%AE%A2-%E9%AB%AE%E5%9E%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%8B%B8%E8%AE%93%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E6%8E%80%E7%BD%B5%E6%88%B0-104906536.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/u4mFAELrKdbg0SuOdQBvMA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/d0997554c0476b03dfbd971b9860778e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fu4mFAELrKdbg0SuOdQBvMA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fd0997554c0476b03dfbd971b9860778e&h=94c01860&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=bdbb490e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】人人都趕在過年前理個髮，迎接新一年。髮型屋也大排長龍，昨日(4日)一名男子在髮型屋輪候理髮時，疑等站立位置與髮型師展開爭執，雙方「你一言，我一語」，互不相讓，幾乎提早「開年」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事件發生於天水圍一間商場內快速剪髮店，上載影片的網民指，當時男子站於店舖門口輪候，「之後個位職員叫個客人出去等，唔好企喺門口阻住其他客人」，不過此舉卻惹男子不滿，出言謾罵髮型師，髮型師亦不示弱，反駁說：「我依家唔做你生意」，結果演變成二人互罵場面。雙方唇槍舌劍再夾雜粗言穢語，使其他在場人士感無奈，只好默不作聲，現場氣氛十分緊張，直至商場保安到場調停，事件才平息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民怒斥男子「為小事聲大大」十分無禮，「依家聲大、講粗口就大晒？」「畀幾十蚊以為自己大晒？」有網民戲謔男子鬧事「唔識死」，「一陣畀人剪到一忽忽，唔好問點解！」「寧得罪小人，莫得罪髮型師啊！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n得罪髮型師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3e6952a1a1b7049c114f09c4febf029131aea1","tid":1010524,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T05:07:22.000Z","msg":"髮型師應該照幫佢剪<br />\n但唔小心剪到一忽忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11fa97c7e0708215ce215c5b8979aa89f75aaade","tid":1010524,"uid":3138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T06:02:50.000Z","msg":"剪緊嗰個實淆到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}